June 19 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Thursday. To inform us of other job changes, email to moves@thomsonreuters.com.

CITIGROUP INC <C.N> The U.S. bank named Mark Slaughter as Asia-Pacific head of corporate and investment banking (CIB). Slaughter was previously Citigroup's chief operating officer of CIB globally. He succeeds Farhan Faruqui, who left last month to join Australia and New Zealand Banking Group Ltd <ANZ.AX>. [ID:nL4N0P00RT]  SECURE TRUST BANK PLC <STBS.L>